text: Rääkkylä () is a municipality in North Karelia, Finland. As of 31 December 2023, 1,902 people lived there. Neighbouring municipalities are Joensuu, Kitee, Liperi, Savonlinna and Tohmajärvi. Rääkkylä was founded in 1874. == Other websites == * Municipality of Rääkkylä – Official website Category:Municipalities of North Karelia Category:1874 establishments in Europe Category:1870s establishments in Finland
